{
  "title": "ISic003433. Epitaph for Belleia Vesonia",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Michael Economou</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span> ❦ D(is) · M(anibus) · ❦ <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"BelleiaVelleia · Vesonia\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"BelleiaVelleia\">Belleia</span> · <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Vesonia\">Vesonia</span></span> · vix(it) · <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span> ann(is) · XXXIIII´ · <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Lucius\">L(ucius)</span> · <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ostrius\">Ostrius</span> · <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Crescens\">Crescens</span> · uxori · rarissimae · </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\">l.2 reg., orig. BELLEIABelleia</p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Michael Economou</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>❦DM❦<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"BelleiaVelleia · Vesonia\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"BelleiaVelleia\">BELLEIA</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Vesonia\">VESONIA</span></span>VIX<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ANNXXXIIII<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Lucius\">L</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ostrius\">OSTRIUS</span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Crescens\">CRESCENS</span>UXORIRARISSIMAE</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\">l.2 reg., orig. BELLEIABelleia</p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003433_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003433_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003433.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003433-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text based upon Bitto 2001 and controlled against photograph</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">Michael Economou</p>  <p>To the shades of the underworld. Belleia Vesonia lived for 34 years. Lucius Ostrius Crescens for his extraordinary wife.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Orsi 1916 133 fig.8 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001701\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001701</a></li><li> Bitto 2001 1 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000029\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000029</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>Neatly v-cut letters, with faint traces of guidelines. The letters have deep serifs at the end of strokes: E is often very narrow, with the horizontal bars angled upwards; M and A in the final line have extended upper strokes, tending towards cursive; interpuncts are variable in form.</p> Line 1  27  Lines 2-4  30  Interlineation lines 1 to 4  8-11  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
